1
00:01:07,800 --> 00:01:10,080
All the sorrows between you and me.

2
00:01:22,640 --> 00:01:23,360
Sister.

3
00:01:24,320 --> 00:01:25,480
I asked around.

4
00:01:25,800 --> 00:01:28,200
Sister Hui has seen this bamboo curtain.

5
00:01:28,560 --> 00:01:29,440
Only Xiong Renlian,

6
00:01:29,440 --> 00:01:31,240
Official Xiong, has one at home.

7
00:01:31,240 --> 00:01:33,360
Xiong Renlian's bamboo mat.

8
00:01:36,440 --> 00:01:38,240
Such a private item.

9
00:01:39,560 --> 00:01:41,420
How would Sister Hui have seen it?

10
00:01:43,800 --> 00:01:45,039
She is a poor soul.

11
00:01:45,320 --> 00:01:47,039
The wives and daughters of these salt worker families,

12
00:01:47,039 --> 00:01:50,300
which of them hasn't been abused by that dog of an official?

13
00:01:52,039 --> 00:01:54,520
These petty officials in the salt administration,

14
00:01:54,520 --> 00:01:57,920
really think they're emperors, doing whatever they please.

15
00:01:59,640 --> 00:02:00,960
When we leave,

16
00:02:01,040 --> 00:02:02,700
we'll take Sister Hui with us.

17
00:02:03,160 --> 00:02:06,200
Most of the salt workers here are descendants of criminals.

18
00:02:06,200 --> 00:02:08,800
Sent here by the authorities to boil salt as hard labor.

19
00:02:08,800 --> 00:02:10,880
Their household registration is strictly for salt work.

20
00:02:10,880 --> 00:02:13,120
A hereditary lowly status for generations.

21
00:02:13,120 --> 00:02:15,580
Their status is as low as government slaves.

22
00:02:18,200 --> 00:02:20,930
Salt workers are registered by the authorities.

23
00:02:21,640 --> 00:02:22,800
Once you're on the register,

24
00:02:22,800 --> 00:02:24,329
you can't go anywhere else,

25
00:02:24,800 --> 00:02:26,000
or change your trade.

26
00:02:26,640 --> 00:02:28,900
Boiling salt is your only way to survive.

27
00:02:30,200 --> 00:02:31,160
Just like...

28
00:02:35,760 --> 00:02:37,160
It won't be like that, Yan'er.

29
00:02:37,160 --> 00:02:38,240
You are different.

30
00:02:40,360 --> 00:02:41,200
Trust me.

31
00:02:41,760 --> 00:02:43,640
I will find a way

32
00:02:43,640 --> 00:02:45,440
to let you live the life you want.

33
00:02:58,040 --> 00:03:00,800
The Imperial Envoy for the Witchcraft Case.

34
00:03:01,440 --> 00:03:04,040
What the hell does my business have to do with the Witchcraft Case?

35
00:03:04,040 --> 00:03:07,840
I'm just taking advantage of the chaos to sell a few more bags of salt.

36
00:03:08,360 --> 00:03:09,480
Uncle.

37
00:03:10,600 --> 00:03:14,040
You've been Governor for so many years.

38
00:03:14,520 --> 00:03:17,120
Why are you more timid than me?

39
00:03:17,560 --> 00:03:18,360
Who's there?

40
00:03:28,120 --> 00:03:29,000
Sister.

41
00:03:32,520 --> 00:03:34,040
Official Xiong is dead.

42
00:03:34,520 --> 00:03:35,240
What?

43
00:03:37,079 --> 00:03:38,540
Xiong Renlian is dead too.

44
00:03:40,440 --> 00:03:43,120
Ouch.

45
00:03:46,880 --> 00:03:48,160
You're so clumsy.

46
00:03:49,640 --> 00:03:51,640
If you really become a cripple,

47
00:03:52,040 --> 00:03:53,520
what will you do then?

48
00:03:53,520 --> 00:03:54,680
You're the cripple.

49
00:03:54,680 --> 00:03:55,720
Don't jinx me.

50
00:03:56,680 --> 00:03:58,520
I went to the market this morning.

51
00:03:58,520 --> 00:04:00,400
I heard everyone talking about it.

52
00:04:00,400 --> 00:04:02,060
They described it so vividly,

53
00:04:02,520 --> 00:04:03,720
saying he bashed his head against a wall.

54
00:04:03,720 --> 00:04:05,280
Bashed his head?

55
00:04:07,680 --> 00:04:08,480
Wait.

56
00:04:09,640 --> 00:04:10,920
Are you going to the crime scene?

57
00:04:10,920 --> 00:04:11,880
I want to go too.

58
00:04:12,880 --> 00:04:13,520
You want to go?

59
00:04:13,520 --> 00:04:14,320
Yeah.

60
00:04:14,840 --> 00:04:17,480
Can you make it, limping like that?

61
00:04:18,440 --> 00:04:20,440
It's just a scratch.

62
00:04:20,600 --> 00:04:22,800
As long as I don't put too much pressure on it, I'm fine.

63
00:04:22,800 --> 00:04:23,840
See?

64
00:04:25,080 --> 00:04:25,520
Look.

65
00:04:25,680 --> 00:04:26,520
Let me go too.

66
00:04:28,240 --> 00:04:30,170
Miss Yan'er, you should stay home.

67
00:04:30,800 --> 00:04:33,240
If Sister Hui comes back and finds no one home,

68
00:04:33,240 --> 00:04:34,300
she'll be worried.

69
00:04:35,680 --> 00:04:36,920
Yan'er, why don't you just

70
00:04:36,920 --> 00:04:37,980
wait for me at home?

71
00:04:38,080 --> 00:04:39,520
I'll bring you a roast chicken from Li's when I get back.

72
00:04:39,520 --> 00:04:41,200
It's delicious, okay?

73
00:04:41,880 --> 00:04:43,540
Then I'll wait for you at home.

74
00:04:46,320 --> 00:04:47,520
- Let's go.
- Let's go.

75
00:04:58,920 --> 00:05:00,120
Walk faster.

76
00:05:00,400 --> 00:05:01,640
I'm faster than you.

77
00:05:16,440 --> 00:05:19,370
Xiong Renlian has already been placed in his coffin.

78
00:05:20,080 --> 00:05:22,400
Official Xiong's death is too suspicious.

79
00:05:22,400 --> 00:05:24,460
With the recent witchcraft scare...

80
00:05:24,640 --> 00:05:26,880
The other masters of the Xiong family were afraid the corpse would reanimate.

81
00:05:26,880 --> 00:05:28,560
So they had it burned to ashes.

82
00:05:32,520 --> 00:05:35,400
We arrived too late. The body and the scene are gone.

83
00:05:41,040 --> 00:05:42,800
That house by the burial mounds,

84
00:05:42,800 --> 00:05:45,000
there must be something fishy about it.

85
00:06:23,080 --> 00:06:25,320
I didn't expect that beneath this house,

86
00:06:25,320 --> 00:06:27,580
there would actually be hidden secrets.

87
00:06:29,120 --> 00:06:30,720
Impressive, Lord Fang.

88
00:06:33,320 --> 00:06:34,120
Let's go.

89
00:06:39,720 --> 00:06:40,320
Slow down.

90
00:07:08,960 --> 00:07:09,820
Young Marquis.

91
00:07:10,320 --> 00:07:12,780
According to the secret letter Miss Gu sent,

92
00:07:12,960 --> 00:07:13,760
they should be

93
00:07:14,560 --> 00:07:16,360
right near these burial mounds.

94
00:07:16,360 --> 00:07:17,620
It gives me the creeps.

95
00:07:19,720 --> 00:07:20,920
Let's check up ahead.

96
00:07:21,280 --> 00:07:21,960
Hyah!

97
00:07:22,560 --> 00:07:23,160
Hyah!

98
00:07:36,280 --> 00:07:37,840
Why won't this door open?

99
00:07:40,400 --> 00:07:41,330
Is anyone there?

100
00:07:41,680 --> 00:07:42,610
Is anyone there?

101
00:07:43,159 --> 00:07:43,960
Open the door!

102
00:07:44,440 --> 00:07:46,080
Hey! Is anyone there?

103
00:07:47,280 --> 00:07:48,140
Stop shouting.

104
00:07:48,920 --> 00:07:50,520
There shouldn't be anyone here.

105
00:07:50,520 --> 00:07:51,520
Then what do we do?

106
00:07:59,360 --> 00:08:00,820
Oh no. There's a trap here.

107
00:08:08,320 --> 00:08:09,780
Cover your mouth and nose.

108
00:08:10,000 --> 00:08:11,130
I'll go find an exit.

109
00:08:11,480 --> 00:08:13,080
Wait here for me. Don't move.

110
00:08:18,040 --> 00:08:19,000
Be careful.

111
00:08:20,000 --> 00:08:21,200
Keep up, quickly.

112
00:08:26,000 --> 00:08:26,800
Search!

113
00:08:28,160 --> 00:08:29,160
Search the place!

114
00:08:30,800 --> 00:08:31,400
Hurry.

115
00:08:32,000 --> 00:08:32,600
This way.

116
00:08:32,720 --> 00:08:33,520
Come on.

117
00:08:33,640 --> 00:08:34,039
Come.

118
00:08:34,679 --> 00:08:35,080
Hurry.

119
00:08:35,840 --> 00:08:36,299
Faster.

120
00:08:36,400 --> 00:08:37,200
Nothing here.

121
00:08:39,720 --> 00:08:40,250
This way.

122
00:08:41,280 --> 00:08:42,480
You go check over there.

123
00:08:42,480 --> 00:08:43,010
Yes, sir.

124
00:08:45,080 --> 00:08:45,680
Hurry up.

125
00:09:01,760 --> 00:09:02,360
Move.

126
00:09:02,920 --> 00:09:03,960
Nothing on my side.

127
00:09:03,960 --> 00:09:05,090
It's empty here too.

128
00:09:05,760 --> 00:09:06,560
We've searched everywhere,

129
00:09:06,560 --> 00:09:07,760
but we found nothing.

130
00:09:08,160 --> 00:09:10,360
Could we be in the wrong place?

131
00:09:20,160 --> 00:09:20,960
Follow me.

132
00:09:32,960 --> 00:09:33,800
Young Marquis.

133
00:09:33,800 --> 00:09:34,640
How about

134
00:09:34,800 --> 00:09:36,730
we search the surroundings again?

135
00:09:40,520 --> 00:09:41,720
I feel like

136
00:09:42,240 --> 00:09:43,480
she is right near me.

137
00:10:07,600 --> 00:10:08,600
Gu Lihan!

138
00:10:11,800 --> 00:10:14,560
Gu Lihan, are you in there?

139
00:10:31,440 --> 00:10:32,440
Gu Lihan!

140
00:10:37,400 --> 00:10:38,260
Young Marquis!

141
00:10:39,120 --> 00:10:39,650
Gu Lihan!

142
00:10:41,240 --> 00:10:42,160
Save them, quickly!

143
00:10:42,160 --> 00:10:42,880
Yes, sir.

144
00:11:01,240 --> 00:11:02,160
Sister, you're awake.

145
00:11:02,160 --> 00:11:03,560
I'll pour you some water.

146
00:11:13,520 --> 00:11:14,440
Fang...

147
00:11:15,000 --> 00:11:16,280
Where is Lord Fang?

148
00:11:21,400 --> 00:11:22,680
How is he?

149
00:11:23,200 --> 00:11:24,860
Lord Fang hasn't woken up yet.

150
00:11:25,680 --> 00:11:26,740
He hasn't woken up?

151
00:11:29,960 --> 00:11:31,360
But don't worry, Sister.

152
00:11:31,520 --> 00:11:33,400
The Young Marquis already called a doctor.

153
00:11:33,400 --> 00:11:36,000
He has treated the poison for you and Lord Fang.

154
00:11:36,080 --> 00:11:37,280
Okay.

155
00:11:42,400 --> 00:11:43,760
I'll go check on him.

156
00:11:45,720 --> 00:11:46,960
Sister!

157
00:12:00,240 --> 00:12:02,700
You really have nothing better to do, do you?

158
00:12:03,760 --> 00:12:04,620
Young Marquis.

159
00:12:04,840 --> 00:12:06,120
Rabbit blood dispels cold.

160
00:12:06,120 --> 00:12:09,250
Prepare a bowl of rabbit blood soup for Miss Gu's dinner.

161
00:12:10,760 --> 00:12:11,290
Yes, sir.

162
00:12:12,280 --> 00:12:13,640
Oh, by the way, Young Marquis,

163
00:12:13,640 --> 00:12:15,840
I just saw...

164
00:12:15,840 --> 00:12:18,000
Miss Gu entered Master Fang's room.

165
00:12:27,360 --> 00:12:29,200
Rabbit blood dispels cold.

166
00:12:39,240 --> 00:12:39,720
Fang Ji.

167
00:12:49,440 --> 00:12:51,040
Didn't he take the antidote?

168
00:12:51,360 --> 00:12:52,820
Why hasn't he woken up yet?

169
00:12:58,680 --> 00:12:59,720
He's burning up.

170
00:13:24,080 --> 00:13:24,880
Let me.

171
00:13:41,080 --> 00:13:46,160
A misty rain, a dream.

172
00:13:47,880 --> 00:13:53,040
Moonlight sings to the cool breeze.

173
00:13:53,880 --> 00:13:57,080
Flowers bloom in the silent night, persistence remains.

174
00:13:57,680 --> 00:14:00,680
Yesterday, the youth made a promise.

175
00:14:01,480 --> 00:14:02,560
It is to love,

176
00:14:03,000 --> 00:14:06,400
penning a profound page.

177
00:14:08,400 --> 00:14:10,200
A tune of qin and se, a pot of wine.

178
00:14:11,440 --> 00:14:11,520
Sharing the song and wine.

179
00:14:11,520 --> 00:14:13,440
A tune of qin and se, a pot of wine.
